{"tid":2126520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳深夜通報  港確診司機曾逗留羅湖住所","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T04:56:47.000Z","uid":240448,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"af820bd06aa235e432b1db8822d787456c61a425","tid":2126520,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"深圳羅湖區新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部昨深夜發佈通告，指同日下午接獲香港衞生防護中心通報，一名朱姓香港貨車司機在港確診武漢肺炎。經查，朱男按照相關豁免政策規定，於7月18日晚上8時31分從文錦渡口岸入境，入境時核酸檢測為陰性；22日晚上7時26分從文錦渡口岸返回香港，26日確診。<br />\n<br />\n經流行病學調查，朱男曾在位於羅湖區蓮塘街道畔山花園屋苑的住所逗留。為落實疫情常態化防控工作「應檢盡檢」相關要求，即日起對該屋苑全體居民進行免費核酸檢測。該疫情防控指揮部呼籲居民加強個人日常防護措施，如有不適應及時到就近發熱門診就醫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200727/I4X2SCG42AWB5DSCLAFL5GZAO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200727%2FI4X2SCG42AWB5DSCLAFL5GZAO4%2F&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=91af89c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200727%2FI4X2SCG42AWB5DSCLAFL5GZAO4%2F&h=14958b61\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200727/I4X2SCG42AWB5DSCLAFL5GZAO4/</a>"},{"pid":"7100d4f869eed01bd9642e2bf6ff0afcb1c83eaa","tid":2126520,"uid":240448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"香港司機曾逗留羅湖住所，全屋苑居民需要接受檢測。 (互聯網)"},{"pid":"f968e8ddf3133b85ae1ade565b43607d791a64df","tid":2126520,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07f7d2cc402b354768029e4366d533fc9942fb8","tid":2126520,"uid":3980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"羅湖哩啲地區當佢係中國都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1cc972512dbf0d26733cd6ee00d9e3fc3b028d